data.horoscope_data: The next several weeks will have you wearing rose-colored glasses now that Neptune is in Aries and your home zone. While you want to be close to your family and build a dream home for yourself, you might not be looking at the facts. Be careful where you put down roots, Capricorn. The foundation might not be solid.Fortunately, the weekend is ideal for relationships when Mars in Cancer trines Saturn in Pisces on Friday. This is a great time to have important conversations in your relationships so everyone is on the same page. From having “what are we?” talks to diving into new responsibilities, show how much you care today.Working together with loved ones can lead to amazing things when Venus in Pisces trines Mars on Sunday. This is a great day to find a partner in crime to take on the world.
